activity_state.help:
Status based on activities
Overdue: Due date is already passed
Today: Activity date is today
Planned: Future activities.

activity_exception_decoration.help: Type of the exception activity on record.

activity_exception_icon.help: Icon to indicate an exception activity.

message_needaction.help: If checked, new messages require your attention.

message_has_error.help: If checked, some messages have a delivery error.

message_has_error_counter.help: Number of messages with delivery error

message_has_sms_error.help: If checked, some messages have a delivery error.

is_storno.help: Utility field to express whether the journal item is subject to storno accounting

cumulated_balance.help: Cumulated balance depending on the domain and the order chosen in the view.

currency_rate.help: Currency rate from company currency to document currency.

amount_currency.help: The amount expressed in an optional other currency if it is a multi-currency entry.

payment_id.help: The payment that created this entry

statement_line_id.help: The statement line that created this entry

statement_id.help: The bank statement used for bank reconciliation

tax_line_id.help: Indicates that this journal item is a tax line

tax_repartition_line_id.help: Tax distribution line that caused the creation of this move line, if any

tax_tag_ids.help: Tags assigned to this line by the tax creating it, if any. It determines its impact on financial reports.

amount_residual.help: The residual amount on a journal item expressed in the company currency.

amount_residual_currency.help: The residual amount on a journal item expressed in its currency (possibly not the company currency).

matched_debit_ids.help: Debit journal items that are matched with this journal item.

matched_credit_ids.help: Credit journal items that are matched with this journal item.

matching_number.help: Matching number for this line, 'P' if it is only partially reconcile, or the name of the full reconcile if it exists.

is_account_reconcile.help: Check this box if this account allows invoices & payments matching of journal items.

account_type.help: Account Type is used for information purpose, to generate country-specific legal reports, and set the rules to close a fiscal year and generate opening entries.

product_uom_category_id.help: Conversion between Units of Measure can only occur if they belong to the same category. The conversion will be made based on the ratios.

quantity.help: The optional quantity expressed by this line, eg: number of product sold. The quantity is not a legal requirement but is very useful for some reports.

date_maturity.help: This field is used for payable and receivable journal entries. You can put the limit date for the payment of this line.

discount_date.help: Last date at which the discounted amount must be paid in order for the Early Payment Discount to be granted

blocked.help: You can check this box to mark this journal item as a litigation with the associated partner

deferred_start_date.help: Date at which the deferred expense/revenue starts

deferred_end_date.help: Date at which the deferred expense/revenue ends

expected_pay_date.help: Expected payment date as manually set through the customer statement(e.g: if you had the customer on the phone and want to remember the date he promised he would pay)

next_action_date.help: Date where the next action should be taken for a receivable item. Usually, automatically set when sending reminders through the customer statement.

invoice_origin.help: The document(s) that generated the invoice.

product_type.help:
A storable product is a product for which you manage stock. The Inventory app has to be installed.
A consumable product is a product for which stock is not managed.
A service is a non-material product you provide.

selection: 0 - Nacional, exceto as indicadas nos códigos 3, 4, 5 e 8;

3 - Nacional, mercadoria ou bem com Conteúdo de Importação superior a 40% e inferior ou igual a 70%;

5 - Nacional, mercadoria ou bem com Conteúdo de Importação inferior ou igual a 40%;
6 - Estrangeira - Importação direta, sem similar nacional, constante em lista da CAMEX e gás natural;
7 - Estrangeira - Adquirida no mercado interno, sem similar nacional, constante lista CAMEX e gás natural.
8 - Nacional, mercadoria ou bem com Conteúdo de Importação superior a 70%;
